{"tid":128442,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[現正招攬]木結他初心者whatsapp gp","createTime":"2017-02-20T22:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T18:10:28.000Z","uid":69486,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc45f935248279846275d54e0f52fa06a2add98","tid":128442,"uid":69486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T22:47:04.000Z","msg":"本群成立左一年左右，<br />\n係高登開post 成立，到而家開到黎連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續為大家堅守音樂台木結他實力最低層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地不問男女，不問年紀，<br />\n總之你有興趣，而又係真。新手我地就無任歡迎<br />\n另外我地會定期清人，確保成員間有良好嘅互動<br />\n<br />\n假如你對木結他充滿熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而又有興趣加入的話，請填妥以下google form:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeJTiGFdp8xNyhCBNDh9GJQgKBOv-3hTnRqM5hRRxOZNanEkw/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeJTiGFdp8xNyhCBNDh9GJQgKBOv-3hTnRqM5hRRxOZNanEkw%2Fviewform%3Fc%3D0%26w%3D1&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=50166229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeJTiGFdp8xNyhCBNDh9GJQgKBOv-3hTnRqM5hRRxOZNanEkw/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1</a><br />\n<br />\n收到表格後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋入境署嘅同事會盡快whatsapp 你"},{"pid":"d8ba8f388c06e10ffafa9620425aae096088abd5","tid":128442,"uid":2966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T22:50:36.000Z","msg":"入唔到電話"},{"pid":"57e9b98daa3cef9c3dde800470cead1b03c4def2","tid":128442,"uid":24264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T23:21:52.000Z","msg":"電話當email填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f344497c9f7cbee3e53646737efe9add6919ac7","tid":128442,"uid":69486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T00:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入唔到電話</bloc